</div>
<button class="accordion">Why is conflict management training important?
</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>Conflict management training is beneficial in the reduction of conflict in the workplace. It can improve employee productivity and loyalty. Also, it can help alleviate stress and absenteeism.
</p>
</div>
